1. **Critical (Pan gesture / ScrollView conflict, line 509)** — the `activateAfterLongPress(120)` approach will not reliably compete with the native `ScrollView` scroll gesture. The mobile-mcp AC ("drag, observe loading") will fail. Needs `activateOffsetY` with proper gesture composition.

